  <div id="yylybanner">Temperature Controllers</div>

  <div id="div0">
    <p>Ferrotec&rsquo;s FTC-series of TEC temperature controllers are specially designed for the unique requirements of systems and applications that use peltier coolers for precision temperature control. As a leading supplier of thermoelectric modules, we recognized our customers&rsquo; need for an easy-to-use solution for developing, building, and mass-producing thermal control systems for their TEC application. FTC-series controllers start with cost-effective PWM-based PID controllers with auto-tune and support for bi-directional power control. Next we add sophisticated features like support for programmable scripting for advanced temperature management functionality. Finally, we roll it all up into a flexible, component-based solution that can be integrated directly into your production system.</p>
  </div>

