    <p id="titledetail">
      <a href="/content/ftc100">
      <b>Ferrotec's FTC100 Temperature Controller with Panel Interface&nbsp;&raquo;</b>
      </a>
    </p>
    <p id="cpjjsummary"> The FTC100 incorporates a LED display and a panel interface, enabling users to monitor the controller and change settings using buttons on the front of the panel display. The FTC100 also supports configuration using a computer and its integrated RS232 interface. </p>
    <p id="cpjjsummary"><b>&nbsp;&raquo;&nbsp;The FTC100 is a perfect fit for most TEC temperature control applications.</b></p>
