    <b>Ferrotec's FTC200 Temperature Controller for Embedded Applications&nbsp;&raquo;</b>
    </a>
  </p>
  <p id="cpjjsummary">The FTC200 is designed to streamline the process of integrating sophisticated precision temperature control into your volume production system. The FTC200 offers some advanced temperature control features, but can only be configured and monitored through its communications interface using a computer. </p>
